<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset</title>
    {{EmailStyle}}
</head>

<body>
    <p>Hello,</p>
    <p>We received a request to reset the password for your <strong>{{.OrganizationName}}</strong> account.</p>
    <p>Click the button below to create a new password:</p>
    <p><a href="{{.ResetPasswordLink}}" class="button">Reset Password</a></p>
    <p>If you didn't request this password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password won't be
        changed unless you click the button above.</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br>
        The <strong>{{.OrganizationName}}</strong> Team</p>
</body>

</html>